					<description><![CDATA[Costa Rica has established itself as a regional leader in attracting investment and strengthening the entrepreneurial ecosystem. The driving force behind this progress lies not only in macroeconomic figures, but also in the human connections behind each project. To continue building on its momentum of growth and recognition, San José is preparing to host a [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>Costa Rica has established itself as a regional leader in attracting investment and strengthening the entrepreneurial ecosystem. The driving force behind this progress lies not only in macroeconomic figures, but also in the human connections behind each project.</p>



<p>To continue building on its momentum of growth and recognition, San José is preparing to host a new edition of <a href="https://inhaus.my.canva.site/speed-dating">Talent Speed Dating</a> on March 13. This unique format, driven by INHAUS, is designed to generate meaningful conversations, break down traditional recruitment barriers, and transform the way companies and professionals discover one another.</p>



<p>Unlike conventional selection processes, Talent Speed Dating features strategic 15-minute interviews, where the primary goal is to connect high-potential candidates with organizations that seek not only technical skills but also a genuine alignment in vision and culture. It is a space designed to create opportunities that go beyond a specific job opening, fostering long-term connections within the business ecosystem.</p>



<p>The success of this methodology is backed by tangible results in the region; following a highly successful event in Panama in 2025, where over 890 candidates were evaluated and more than 280 simultaneous interviews were conducted, the event arrives in Costa Rica with the promise of continuing to make an impact.</p>



<p>The previous experience demonstrated that face-to-face, agile, and human interaction is the most powerful tool for high-value networking, allowing companies to access pre-screened talent and enabling professionals to interact directly with the leaders shaping the industry.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-what-to-expect-from-talent-speed-dating-in-san-jose"><strong>What to expect from Talent Speed Dating in San José?</strong></h2>



<p>The event is designed for professionals who are not only looking for a job but also want to lead change in their respective fields. The agenda for March 2026 has been carefully structured to offer a comprehensive experience:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>High-impact networking:</strong> Spaces specifically designed to break the ice and build strategic relationships with decision-makers in the ecosystem.</li>



<li><strong>Talent Speed Dating:</strong> Rounds of one-on-one conversations with tech companies and multinationals expanding their operations in Costa Rica.</li>



<li><strong>Mentors and Speakers</strong>: Practical talks and inspiring sessions on Artificial Intelligence, modern leadership, and the trends that are redefining the global job market.</li>



<li><strong>Professional Growth:</strong> Workshops focused on how to successfully navigate the evolution of professional careers in the era of automation and digitalization.</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-synergy-between-companies-and-talent-as-a-driver-of-change"><strong>Synergy between companies and talent as a driver of change</strong></h2>



<p>In the age of technology, human connection remains, without a doubt, the ultimate competitive advantage. INHAUS Talent Speed Dating goes beyond interviews; it is an immersive experience where the efficiency of personalized schedules blends with moments of deep inspiration. </p>



<p>Attendees will be able to connect with key figures in the sector, sharing best practices and discovering where the market is headed.</p>



<p>The event will feature high-growth organizations and tech giants that view Costa Rican talent as key to driving global innovation. For participating companies, this edition represents a platform for strategic visibility and a unique opportunity to strengthen their employer brand among the country’s most prominent professionals.</p>



<p>Those interested in participating can register for free on the <a href="https://inhaus.my.canva.site/speed-dating">official website</a> and be part of this movement that seeks to redefine the future of work in Costa Rica. </p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
