										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>The healthcare and pharmaceutical industries are under growing pressure to communicate complex scientific, clinical, and regulatory information with greater speed and accuracy. As organizations expand globally, internal teams face mounting demands to align data, compliance requirements, and decision-making across regions and functions.</p>



<p>Within this context, <a href="https://www.prezent.ai/">Prezent</a> has positioned itself as a provider of AI-driven tools designed to streamline business communications. The company focuses on helping large organizations standardize and accelerate the creation of presentations and executive materials.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="668" src="http://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-1024x668.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-90743" srcset="https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-1024x668.jpg 1024w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-300x196.jpg 300w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-768x501.jpg 768w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-1536x1003.jpg 1536w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-332x217.jpg 332w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-664x433.jpg 664w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-688x449.jpg 688w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-1376x898.jpg 1376w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-1045x682.jpg 1045w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine-1400x914.jpg 1400w, https://contxto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/marine.jpg 1765w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><em>Marine Queniart Stojanovic</em></figcaption></figure>



<p>Against this backdrop, Prezent announced that <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/marine-queniart-stojanovic">Marine Queniart Stojanovic</a> has joined its Senior Executive Board. She joins other board members with experience spanning technology, healthcare, and corporate governance.</p>



<p>Queniart Stojanovic brings more than 25 years of global leadership experience from GSK and Sanofi, where she held senior roles across commercial operations, general management, and digital transformation in the US, Europe, and Southeast Asia.</p>



<p>Her career includes leading large, multi-country teams and overseeing transformation initiatives focused on modernizing commercial and medical engagement models, as well as integrating digital and data-driven approaches into enterprise operations.</p>



<p>According to <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rajatbmishra/">Rajat Mishra</a>, CEO and co-founder of Prezent, life sciences organizations require deep domain expertise to meaningfully improve communication workflows. He said Queniart Stojanovic’s perspective will help guide the company’s next phase of growth in regulated industries.</p>



<p>The appointment comes as Prezent continues expanding its enterprise AI platform, including the recent launch of an API aimed at automating on-brand presentations for clinical updates, regulatory briefings, and executive communications within healthcare and life sciences organizations.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
